OL,5, Labour is calling for a parliamentary  
OL,6, investigation into Boris Johnson after 
OL,7, claims the chairman of the BBC helped  
OL,8, the former PM secure a loan - weeks    
OL,9, before he recommended him for the role.
OL,11,FAccording to the Sunday Times, BBC     
OL,12,Fchairman Richard Sharp helped arrange a
OL,13,Fguarantee on a loan of up to #800,000  
OL,14,Ffor Mr Johnson.                        
OL,16,FMr Johnson called the story "rubbish". 
OL,18,FAnd Mr Sharp said there was a not a    
OL,19,Fconflict as he "simply connected" the  
OL,20,Fpeople involved in the loan.           
